ivardefs.name: basedOn_
ivardefs.desc: An order, proposal or plan fulfilled in whole or in part by this Communication.

ivardefs.name: category_
ivardefs.desc: The type of message conveyed such as alert, notification, reminder, instruction, etc.

ivardefs.name: context
ivardefs.desc: The encounter within which the communication was sent.

ivardefs.name: definition_
ivardefs.desc: A protocol, guideline, or other definition that was adhered to in whole or in part by this communication event.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifiers associated with this Communication that are defined by business processes and/ or used to refer to it when a direct URL reference to the resource itself is not appropriate (e.g. in CDA documents, or in written / printed documentation).

ivardefs.name: medium_
ivardefs.desc: A channel that was used for this communication (e.g. email, fax).

ivardefs.name: notDone
ivardefs.desc: If true, indicates that the described communication event did not actually occur.

ivardefs.name: notDoneReason
ivardefs.desc: Describes why the communication event did not occur in coded and/or textual form.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Additional notes or commentary about the communication by the sender, receiver or other interested parties.

ivardefs.name: partOf_
ivardefs.desc: Part of this action.

ivardefs.name: payload_
ivardefs.desc: Text, attachment(s), or resource(s) that was communicated to the recipient.

ivardefs.name: reasonCode_
ivardefs.desc: The reason or justification for the communication.

ivardefs.name: reasonReference_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates another resource whose existence justifies this communication.

ivardefs.name: received
ivardefs.desc: The time when this communication arrived at the destination.

ivardefs.name: recipient_
ivardefs.desc: The entity (e.g. person, organization, clinical information system, or device) which was the target of the communication. If receipts need to be tracked by individual, a separate resource instance will need to be created for each recipient. Â Multiple reci

ivardefs.name: sender
ivardefs.desc: The entity (e.g. person, organization, clinical information system, or device) which was the source of the communication.

ivardefs.name: sent
ivardefs.desc: The time when this communication was sent.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of the transmission.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: The patient or group that was the focus of this communication.

ivardefs.name: topic_
ivardefs.desc: The resources which were responsible for or related to producing this communication.
